    "body": "Requirements as of now(pending questions above):\r\n\r\n- Add dropdown to the first card of the Overview Page which allows the user to select between an \"Eth2 Network\" configuration\r\n- Redux action to set eth2 network value in redux\r\n- Once the user sets the eth2 network, set this name in the `<Appbar/>`\r\n- Refactor all non-private variables in `envVars.ts` to choose from the network config (redux)\r\n- Refactor all references of these variables in the former `envVars.ts` to pull from the new dynamic variable(if redux pull from store)\r\n- Make additional mentions of the network name in all relevant places to ensure a user knows which eth2 network they are on\r\n- Set dynamic contract address on the Summary page\r\n- Update all references to isMainnet to the new config",
