    "body": "To address your questions:\r\n\r\n* **Other eth1 networks:** I think not\r\n* **Custom config support:** Ideally yes, but I don't think this needs to be too complicated: if someone wants to do this, they can manually edit the configs file.\r\n* **Testnet/mainnet swapping once deployed:** I think we can lock it down and if someone want to change, they can be redirected (like block explorers do if you switch networks)\r\n\r\nI think your list of requirements is fairly comprehensive",
